text: "10538 Overture" is a 1972 song by British band Electric Light Orchestra. It is from their first studio album, The Electric Light Orchestra. It went to number 9 in the United Kingdom and number 24 in the Netherlands. ==Jeff Lynne version== Jeff Lynne re-recorded the song in his own home studio for the album Mr. Blue Sky: The Very Best of Electric Light Orchestra. == References == Category:1972 songs Category:Debut singles Category:Electric Light Orchestra songs Category:Def Leppard songs Category:Progressive rock songs
